<item>
            <title>[LU-6404] unable to monut fs through router</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6404</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to mount fs through router the mgs connects but never completes. the client gets this error&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; mount.lustre: mount 10.151.25.251@o2ib:/nbp12k at /nobackuptest failed: Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
Is the MGS running?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;out1.gz is logs from the mds/mgs&lt;br/&gt;
client.out.gz is logs from the client.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-&lt;del&gt;client&lt;/del&gt;-&lt;br/&gt;
r733i3n15 ~ # lctl show_route&lt;br/&gt;
net               o2ib hops 1 gw             10.153.20.77@o2ib233 up pri 0&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;-&lt;del&gt;mgs&lt;/del&gt;-&lt;br/&gt;
service322 ~ # lctl show_route&lt;br/&gt;
net            o2ib233 hops 1 gw                10.151.27.77@o2ib up pri 0&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;--&lt;del&gt;router&lt;/del&gt;--&lt;br/&gt;
maia77 /proc/sys/lnet # cat /sys/module/lnet/parameters/forwarding &lt;br/&gt;
enabled&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;maia77 /proc/sys/lnet # lctl list_nids&lt;br/&gt;
10.151.20.77@o2ib&lt;br/&gt;
10.153.20.77@o2ib233&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
